 StyleBox["v1", "Input"],
 " and ",
 StyleBox["v2", "Input"],
 " are the same, but they have been written in different representations. The \
conversion between two representation can be easily achieved by ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  TemplateBox[{
    Cell[
     TextData["FockCat"]], "paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/ref/FockCat", 
    "QuantumMob Package Symbol"},
