Cell["\<\
Although the representations are different, you can still act operators on \
both form in the usual way:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1623081850,ExpressionUUID->"e6ac312b-955c-4ee5-9967-57db6a33041a"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

